entry.content:
Alva

Having been in New Zealand for nearly 20 years , now it is truly my home . I have experience in media, branding and marketing and my true passion lies in helping businesses by saving time!! I know what a precious commodity it is. Please treat me as you point of call for everything to do with your brand that is what I do best and I will make sure it is right . So if you need branding, with business cards, brochures, signage, apparel orl promotional products , just call, FIOR will sort it!

Jade

In a previous life a Hairdresser, Sales Acc Manager and then Flight Attendant. Recently nearly completed my Bachelors Degree in Toddler Taming with Twin 3 year old Girls. Now thoroughly enjoying my Admin/Support Role in the wonderful Fior Print Team.

Beth

After Graduating from Design & Arts College of New Zealand (D&A) with a Diploma of Communication Arts and Design, I spent a year and a halfÂ  doing freelance design. I now join the Fior team as a graphic designer and am excited to be in this role. My other interests when I am not designing are dance, photography and sewing.
